content: Mei and MK are annoyed to discover that Bai Long Ma's group of rebels aren't as equipped to save Ao Lie as the "real" rebellion. Bai explains that most of them in his group are ex-university students who got in trouble with Spider Queen's minions, and the rebellion took them in to keep them safe - they're still rebels, they just don't have as ready access to the same resources as the "real" rebellion. Let's write that scene with details and dialogue.
